BinomialDeviance <- function(x, p, n)
  
{
  ## x - gene count vector
  ## p - colSums(x)
  ## n - colSums(x).
  term1 <- sum(x*log(x/(n*p)), na.rm=TRUE)
  nx <- n-x
  term2 <- sum(nx*log(nx/(n*(1-p))), na.rm=TRUE)
  return(2*(term1+term2))
  
}

cnts <- counts(combined_sce1)

##Cluster

g <- buildSNNGraph(combined_sce1, k=40, use.dimred="PCA")
